messages.content: I just killed my mom and my sister.
I just killed my mom and my sister.
You just killed your mother and your sister?
I shot them with a .22 revolver.
I want you to stay on the phone with me, okay?
Okay. Hold on just a minute. Where is the gun?
Are you on any kind of medication?
No. Well, I've been going to the allergist lately, but nothing other than that.
You don't take any other kind of medication?
Just Zyrtec and Advil for allergies and headaches.
Is there any reason you were so angry at your mother and your sister?
I wasn't really angry with them. It just kind of happened. I've been planning on killing for a while now.
The two of them or just anybody?
Pretty much anybody. I don't really like people's attitude.
I think people are very rude to each other and stuff like that. My family, I felt like they were suffocating me. I know this is really selfish, but I guess I'm pretty evil.
No, don't be sorry. It's okay. You have my undivided attention.
Were your mom and sister in their beds?
My sister was in her room, and I told her mom needed her. When she came out, I shot her, and she rolled down the stairs. I shot her again, then I went down and shot my mom about three or four times.
You're not sitting by the gun, are you?
No, it's about 10 or 15 feet away from me.
Do you know where he is?
Okay. For future reference, do you want any family members to visit you?
Okay. Where do you go to school, Jake?
I used to go to Ladoga High School, but now I'm homeschooled.
So it's just you, your sister, your mom, and your dad in the house?
Yes, and my grandparents live across the street. My oldest sister lives with them, and I have another sister in college.
Do you want to hurt yourself?
I'm freaked out by guns now. I don't want to hurt myself.
Help will be provided to you, okay? There are people who will help you.
We're here to help you too.
Jake, where is the kitchen in the house? Is it at the back?
Our sergeant is almost at your house. What I'll ask you to do is turn your porch light on. Can you do that?
Jake, do you want to talk about anything else?
Is it a gated community? Do you need a password?
Do you have a driver's license?
It's going to be alright. I'm staying on the phone with you, and they'll be there shortly. Can you go to the front door and turn the porch light on?
I'm just thinking about my sister.
15. She had a sweet side but could be rude to me sometimes.
How long ago did this happen?
You'll be alright, Jake. Just take deep breaths for me. In through your nose and out through your mouth.
Are there any cars in your driveway?
Take deep breaths, Jake. In through your nose, out through your mouth.
